00:28:51.930 --> 00:28:53.099
Pero...

00:28:56.869 --> 00:28:57.910
Nos volveremos a encontrar.

00:28:58.940 --> 00:29:00.039
Cuídate.

00:29:10.150 --> 00:29:11.450
¿Cuál es tu nombre?

00:29:18.690 --> 00:29:21.730
Soy Cho Young.

00:29:40.349 --> 00:29:42.019
